ps:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/image-8-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/image-8-768x354.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/image-8-1536x708.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/image-8-1320x608.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/image-8.png 1920w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/472;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Star Atlas &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.artstation.com\/artwork\/Qxm59Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">GAN Guns Shockwave Pistol<\/a> &#8211; by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.artstation.com\/vertpaint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Vertpaint Studios<\/a> [Concept Art]<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>That is it for this week! Thanks for reading, and until next time!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This week\u2019s update centers on the future of SAGE C4. Beyond further details on the upcoming Phase 2 rollout, Michael shared that the planned off-chain version of C4 is evolving into a full single-player campaign, one that may ultimately replace Holosim as Star Atlas\u2019 primary onboarding experience. We also got new details on z.ink validator licenses, the latest quarterly Economic Report, and an update on the ongoing DAO reimbursement vote.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1}]